    "improvements_made": "Expanded the model to cover all functional areas from the domain description. Added entities for equipment monitoring (ALARM_NOTIFICATION), inspection planning and results (INSPECTION_PLAN, INSPECTION_RECORD), failure reporting (FAILURE_REPORT) and detailed repair workflow (REPAIR_WORK_ORDER, REPAIR_DETAIL). Introduced QUALITY_RECORD and DAILY_QUALITY_REPORT to capture metal recovery rates and grades at both granular and daily levels. Added ROLE for clearer user role management and USER_OPERATION_HISTORY to log user actions. Created JOB_APPLICATION to model the many‑to‑many relationship between USER and JOB_POSITION and to store match rate and application status. Enriched existing entities with foreign keys and additional attributes (e.g., equipment_id in reports, created_by in announcements). Refined relationships with precise cardinalities and descriptive texts, while preserving the original core entities and their strengths."
  }
